snippet.title: Commonplace Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Clock into work and make friends around the office in this small-scale game about ordinary people in an ordinary place. Coming to PC, Mac, and Linux on 8/28/2022.
https://pitter-patter.itch.io/commonplace

Keep up to date with the game on Twitter!
https://twitter.com/PitterPatterDev
